Tyra Banks wants to be your boss. The 90s supermodel and 2000s camp icon has rebranded herself as a financial guru who wants to share her business acumen with young women trying to better their lives. Banks has long fashioned herself as the "relatable supermodel"—an A-lister who repeatedly referred her own "five-head" and implored the media to kiss her fat ass—and this fall she hopes to expand her brand across a variety of platforms: a new beauty venture called Tyra
